Configuration precedence:

1. Capability adapter config in `.joelclaw/config.toml`
2. Process environment
3. `~/.config/system-bus.env`
4. `http://localhost:8123` fallback

The env file resolver is here:

- `packages/sdk/src/lib/otel-ingest.ts:6-19`
- Consumed at `packages/sdk/src/capabilities/adapters/clickhouse-otel.ts:134-143`

Live proof succeeded:

```txt
joelclaw otel search telegram.delivery --hours 24 --limit 1
```

It returned 54 matching events using `adapter: clickhouse-otel`.

